{"repository_id":430564540,"push_id":19592200251,"size":1,"distinct_size":1,"ref":"refs/heads/kf/macrocallsig","head":"761325688037e5e8ff5adb05657bfd009c40063a","before":"5913117b4977fd10895e2c483b3fb9051b5cdf04","commits":[{"sha":"761325688037e5e8ff5adb05657bfd009c40063a","author":{"email":"0d1bb7fa6b1aefd25edab787ad0bbdf687df277d@gmail.com","name":"Claire Foster"},"message":"Make `function (@f(x)) body end` an ambiguity error

This case is ambiguous as it might be either one of the following;
require the user to explicitly disambiguate between them

    function (@f(x),)
        body
    end

    function @f(x)
        body
    end

Also fix parsing of `function (f(x),) end` to correctly emit a tuple.","distinct":true,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/JuliaSyntax.jl/commits/761325688037e5e8ff5adb05657bfd009c40063a"}]}

{"repository_id":430564540,"push_id":19592270138,"size":1,"distinct_size":1,"ref":"refs/heads/kf/macrocallsig","head":"cc303f52be7401ba579ca1fd8eac3cd855cec5e9","before":"761325688037e5e8ff5adb05657bfd009c40063a","commits":[{"sha":"cc303f52be7401ba579ca1fd8eac3cd855cec5e9","author":{"email":"0d1bb7fa6b1aefd25edab787ad0bbdf687df277d@gmail.com","name":"Claire Foster"},"message":"Make `function (@f(x)) body end` an ambiguity error

This case is ambiguous as it might be either one of the following;
require the user to explicitly disambiguate between them

    function (@f(x),)
        body
    end

    function @f(x)
        body
    end

For the same reasons, `function ($f) body end` is also ambiguous.

Also fix parsing of `function (f(x),) end` to correctly emit a tuple.","distinct":true,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/JuliaSyntax.jl/commits/cc303f52be7401ba579ca1fd8eac3cd855cec5e9"}]}

{"repository_id":430564540,"push_id":19592289936,"size":1,"distinct_size":1,"ref":"refs/heads/kf/macrocallsig","head":"398ddf202f004b54020ff31e4138bafc5534666b","before":"cc303f52be7401ba579ca1fd8eac3cd855cec5e9","commits":[{"sha":"398ddf202f004b54020ff31e4138bafc5534666b","author":{"email":"0d1bb7fa6b1aefd25edab787ad0bbdf687df277d@gmail.com","name":"Claire Foster"},"message":"Make `function (@f(x)) body end` an ambiguity error

This case is ambiguous as it might be either one of the following;
require the user to explicitly disambiguate between them

```
function (@f(x),)
    body
end

function @f(x)
    body
end
```

